column5: Hey everyone I was just wondering if anyone who is on Muskies first could take a min and go look at the link below. It is for their lure building contest I have entered they have the top 4 blade baits to be voted on if you can look at them then pic your favourite.  My bait is the white tiger if you feel it looks the best I would love the votes. You can only vote once. If you like one of the others better vote for it but I would love your votes if you feel my bait should win.   http://muskie.outdoorsfirst.com/board/forums/thread-view.asp?tid=101303&posts=2&start=1  Thanks Mike
Didn't get a chance to actually stop by and say hi.  Looks like some beautiful  baits  you had displayed.  Ill try to swing by today
Looking forward to meeting both you guys when i go this afternoon

Mikes stuff is top of the line, and Mike is a great guy. If you're at the show be sure to stop in and check out the baits. He makes awesome eggheads in smaller sized for those who like to chase the pike as well.
